runs.comm: Dawlat starts off with a front foot no-ball, Gambhir pushes it to the off side
Free Hit Vijay's first ball in T20 is scooped high and clean over the bowler and mid-off, it was a slower ball outside off
steers it down to point , thinks of a single but Gambhir sends him back
tucks it to the on side for a single
continues over the wicket, Gambhir opens the face and steers it to third man
VJ! We saw it in the IPL and now again, just a fraction short and he rocks back and pulls crisply over deep midwicket, a spectator takes the catch
attempts a repeat pull but he miscues this one, the ball just eludes the diving mid-on fielder
targets the body and Gambhir turns it to the on side
beats him with a fuller one! Lovely delivery, angles across the right hander, Vijay plays down the wrong line
taps it towards cover, stays back at the crease
bowls with good pace, no speed gun here, Vijay turns it to square leg and sets off, he just manages to beat the throw at the bowler's end
tucked to the on side and Gambhir was in a bit of trouble again with the running, the throw was just wide at the bowler's end
good bounce and carry and well left by Vijay
great stop by Shenwari at backward point, dives to his right and cups his hands behind the ball
caught! Gambhir comes down the track and tries to free his arms by carving it over the off side , he ends up slapping it straight to Nabi at cover point
moves across and punches it away to the off side
full delivery and pushed away very firmly back to the bowler
excellent fielding there, Raina times the cut very well past backward point, Noor sprints from third man and slides and just pulls it back
great commitment in the field again, Raina gets forward to a full delivery and bisects the gap at cover, the fielder chases and pulls it back
short delivery but down the leg side
short again but he opens the face and gently taps it to point
cramps Vijay for room, he stays back and taps it to mid-off, tells Raina to wait
tapped towards extra cover, Zadran's not giving much away here
taps it with soft hands past the bowler and charges off, the fielder at cover Karim Sadiq does his best to collect and have  a shy at the stumps
looks to angle it down to third man but misses
Zadran maintains his discipline again, Raina shows him some respect and defends
tossed up on off, defended back to the bowler
comes down the pitch, checks his shot and taps it to mid-off and sets off
drifts outside leg and he defends
comes down the pitch, gets to the pitch of it and lofts over midwicket, the fielder does well at the deep to try and cut it off but the ball beats him
fails to put away the Free Hit, swings hard but the ball hits his body and rolls away
Raina goes for his favoured slog sweep and he gets the elevation alright and the distance is just enough to clear Stanikzai at deep midwicket
top edges the sweep behind the keeper
good placement by Vijay, Shenwari gives him a bit of width outside off and he opens the face of the bat and cuts past gully and point
tries to cut again but chops it behind the keeper
the quicker one gets him, the ball skids through and hits him low on the pad in front of leg stump, Raina was too lazy in getting his bat behind the line
tucks it behind sqyuare on he on side and a misfield by Dawalat costs a single
tossed up on middle and off and defended
keeps it tight again, defended down the pitch
tossed up outside off and driven to extra cover
on the pads and tucked to square leg
gets forward and pushes it back to the bowler
chips it in the air just wide of short midwicket
turned towards short fine leg and Zadran fails to time his dive properly
comes down the pitch and knocks it down to long-on
the quicker one again, hits his pads but wide of the leg stump, confident appeal
opens the face and angles it down to point for a quick single
down the leg side and Yuvraj tries to paddle it away
stays back and punches it wide of cover
pushes it to long-off
goes back and pulls past square leg, nearly cleans up the umpire, Hasan dives and cuts it off
full outside off and squeezed out to long-on
stays back ans softly drops it to the on side
comes down the track and smartly chips it high in the air over midwicket
works him down to deep midwicket again
fires it quicker and Yuvraj hits it through the line to long-on
fires it flatter and Vijay turns it to long-on
nips back in and the ball hits his pads just above the line of the stumps
stays back and punches it to long-on
nearly cleans him up with a yorker but Vijay just manages to dig it out
hits his thigh and rolls to the off side
the slower ball beats him outside the off stump
bowls the regular quicker one and Yuvraj slashes hard and misses
he oversteps, comes down the track and places it to the on side
full toss for the Free Hit and Yuvraj clubs it away high and far over deep midwicket, more of those will get his confidence back, and it's another no-ball!
Free Hit bowls this really wide outside off
Free Hit This time he comes down the pitch and lofts over extra cover, good work by the boundary rider
defends down the track
nudges it down to square leg
Dropped Vijay comes down the pitch and lofts it high, Hamid Hasan charges from long-off and fluffs the catch on the dive forward
pushes it to the  off side
defended down the pitch
tucked wide of long-on
half volley outside off and elegantly driven down to sweeper cover
full on the stumps and driven down to long-on
pushes the slower ball to cover
clean hit! Vijay gives him the charge, reads the flight and lofts just over long-off
bigger, higher, stronger! Comes down the pitch and slams it over the second tier at long-off
fires it full and he digs it out back to the bowler
driven down to cover
turns it to short midwicket
whips it wide of midwicket
fullish in length on the off stump and pushed to the off side
makes room to scoop it over the bowler's head but he mistimes it to midwicket
driven straight cover
he makes room to dispatch a low full toss but he ends up whacking it flat and quick to Zadran at long-on
bowls a full delivery on the pads and Dhoni clips it to square leg
comes round the wicket to Yuvraj, fires the ball on the pads outside leg
stays back and defends back to the bowler
Dhoni gives him the charge and ensures he clubs it off the meat of the bat, straight over long-off
even higher! In fact he clears his back leg and hits it miles over the sight screen
cuts straight to short third man
angles it just wide of short third man and India stroll through for a seven wicket win
